{"tid":2385980,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"GME新手","createTime":"2021-01-29T10:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T10:46:32.000Z","uid":63548,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"26f86654ad26647b14f99133284827ae56a14a11","tid":2385980,"uid":63548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"好開心第一次玩美股 第一仗就係GME<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解 就算買入價高過依家市價<br />\n<br />\n都有種贏咗既感覺<br />\n<br />\n琴晚睇到佢封盤 有d怯 <br />\n知道一定有唔好既事發生<br />\n至到直插11x<br />\n<br />\n但完全無果種一無所有既感覺<br />\n完全無諗過蝕住走<br />\n唯一做得唔好既係 set左600走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家諗番真係覺得好on9 <br />\n覺得背叛左大家<br />\n<br />\n去到琴晚訓前諗清楚一樣野<br />\n如果佢要咁肉酸 搞到封盤做手腳<br />\n盤中我地除咗賣 咩都做唔到<br />\n重點係比賣唔比買<br />\n機構死壓爛壓 都只係去到11x <br />\n仲要之後彈番上去<br />\n<br />\n平時見到d咩set 1000 或者 10k 100k<br />\n我都係覺得假膠<br />\n但今次先知係我眼光太狹窄<br />\n奴性重 比社會輪慣 <br />\n<br />\n真係睇到我好撚熱血<br />\n今朝唔係比鬧鐘叫醒<br />\n係熱血喚醒<br />\n好精神<br />\n<br />\n果d機構點搞我唔講 始終都係新手<br />\n我仲好想同各位巴打學野<br />\n<br />\n一齊揸緊信念"},{"pid":"c64a5ff07368650bfb6b8cf71bdc458a62e1594d","tid":2385980,"uid":48791,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:02:58.000Z","msg":"新手學野拎呢隻學....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6555d55fd5cea19841f18d2bf4bbbdc55d4055f0","tid":2385980,"uid":226296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"係咪假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5ec0dbb519e8a33fb4d083023599a9f432f5e1","tid":2385980,"uid":149844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:11:40.000Z","msg":"痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一隻玩到咁大"},{"pid":"edea5baf8ba0423ddc21b93275e6224501e5ccf2","tid":2385980,"uid":63548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:12:03.000Z","msg":"起碼見到散戶原來